data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. IMPROVED PRICE! MOTIVATED SELLER! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a pool offers a delightful living experience. The screened pool area exudes elegance with its charming brick pavers, making it perfect for relaxation. Inside, the house features 16" tile flooring throughout, and the kitchen boasts solid wood cottage-style cabinets and stainless steel appliances. NEW Roof only 4 months old., new pool pump and water heater. Additional bar seating in the kitchen invites family and friends to gather and enjoy meals together. The generously sized master suite accommodates a king-size bed and seamlessly connects to the master bathroom, complete with dual sinks and a beautifully tiled, walk-in shower. Outdoors, the property shines with newer landscaping and a private wooded backyard, offering ample space for outdoor entertainment and allowing pets to roam freely. This home truly combines comfort, style, and the joys of outdoor living. Schedule your showing today!
